get events from an artifact set using rcmdcheck::parse_check

get_events.Rd

get events from an artifact set using rcmdcheck::parse_check

get_events(apathset)

Arguments

apathset

instance of artifact_paths

Examples

setup_demo_artifacts()
eg = select_artifacts(paste(tempdir(), "tokay2", sep="/"),
     c("IRanges", "S4V*", "a4\\."))
get_events(eg)
